			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Massive stone blocks rise and fall in shafts near the center of the room.</i></p><p><b>Trap:</b> Depending on its position, each area can be a barrier or a pit, and creatures can also be squashed under several tons of stone.</p>",
